<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 21:10:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于罗纳尔多在迈阿密国际交锋前受伤，纳斯尔推迟了中国友谊赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-nassr-postpone-china-friendlies-ronaldo-injured-before-inter-miami-clash-2024-01-23/</link><description>沙特俱乐部周二表示，克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多(Cristiano Ronaldo)的纳斯尔(Al-Nassr)在前锋受伤后取消了两场中国之旅，这引发了人们对葡萄牙人参加即将对阵莱昂内尔·梅西(Lionel Messi)的迈阿密国际的比赛的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:26:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-nassr-postpone-china-friendlies-ronaldo-injured-before-inter-miami-clash-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>由于希望得到北京方面的支持，在美国上市的中国股市从低点反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-listed-china-stocks-bounce-off-lows-hopes-beijing-support-2024-01-23/</link><description>周二，在纽约上市的中国公司股票在经历了年初的低迷之后反弹，此前有关针对低迷的国内股市的救助计划的报道提振了市场情绪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 16:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-listed-china-stocks-bounce-off-lows-hopes-beijing-support-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>马云第四季度购买了价值 5000 万美元的阿里巴巴股票 - 纽约时报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/jack-ma-bought-alibaba-shares-worth-50-mln-fourth-quarter-nyt-2024-01-23/</link><description>据《纽约时报》周二报道，阿里巴巴联合创始人马云和董事长蔡崇信在第四季度购买了这家中国电子商务巨头价值数百万股的股票，导致该公司在美国上市的股价上涨约 7%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 15:23:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/jack-ma-bought-alibaba-shares-worth-50-mln-fourth-quarter-nyt-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫称中国船只不会在其海域进行研究</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-says-chinese-vessel-will-not-conduct-research-its-waters-2024-01-23/</link><description>马尔代夫外交部周二表示，一艘前往马尔代夫的中国科考船不会在印度洋群岛海域进行任何研究。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 14:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-says-chinese-vessel-will-not-conduct-research-its-waters-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>投资者放弃徒劳地等待中国修复经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/investors-give-up-futile-wait-china-fix-economy-2024-01-23/</link><description>从希望到犹豫，再到现在的彻底投降，中国的全球投资者正纷纷撤离这个世界第二大经济体，并导致中国股市崩盘。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:55:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/investors-give-up-futile-wait-china-fix-economy-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔卡拉斯网球协会为墨尔本兹维列夫考试做准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/tennis-alcaraz-gears-up-zverev-examination-melbourne-2024-01-23/</link><description>二号种子卡洛斯·阿尔卡拉斯周三在墨尔本公园四分之一决赛中对阵德国选手亚历山大·兹维列夫，这无疑将面临澳大利亚网球公开赛中最严峻的考验，这场比赛有望成为一场精彩的风格冲突。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:07:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/tennis-alcaraz-gears-up-zverev-examination-melbourne-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾马科斯表示不支持台独 寻求避免冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-says-does-not-endorse-taiwan-independence-seeks-avoid-2024-01-23/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，他不支持台湾独立，并重申菲律宾致力于一个中国政策，这是对中国对最近祝贺台湾选举获胜者的言论感到愤怒的回应。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 12:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-says-does-not-endorse-taiwan-independence-seeks-avoid-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>宝洁公司强劲的利润率缓解了年度利润预测下调的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/procter-gamble-misses-quarterly-sales-estimates-slowing-china-sales-2024-01-23/</link><description>宝洁公司周二下调了年度利润预期，以反映其吉列业务价值的减记，但该公司第二季度保持健康利润率的能力推动其股价上涨超过 5%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:58:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/procter-gamble-misses-quarterly-sales-estimates-slowing-china-sales-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>3M年度利润预测因电子产品和中国需求低迷而受到挤压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/3m-quarterly-profit-rises-price-hikes-cost-cuts-2024-01-23/</link><description>工业集团 3M 周二预测全年盈利低于华尔街预期，称宏观环境“依然低迷”，导致其股价暴跌约 12%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:36:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/3m-quarterly-profit-rises-price-hikes-cost-cuts-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>意大利希望利用七国集团主席国加强对乌克兰的支持，并审查人工智能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-looks-use-g7-chair-boost-support-ukraine-scrutinise-ai-2024-01-23/</link><description>一位熟悉意大利七国集团计划的消息人士称，意大利将利用七国集团主席国的身份来挑战人们日益增长的看法，即俄罗斯正在乌克兰获胜以及西方已经厌倦了战争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-looks-use-g7-chair-boost-support-ukraine-scrutinise-ai-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>独家：福蒂斯丘中国铁矿石清关面临罕见延误--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/fortescue-faces-rare-delays-china-iron-ore-customs-clearance-sources-2024-01-23/</link><description>据知情人士透露，来自全球第四大供应商福蒂斯丘金属集团的至少两批铁矿石货物在中国北方曹妃甸港因固体废物检查而面临异常海关延误。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/fortescue-faces-rare-delays-china-iron-ore-customs-clearance-sources-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：大型科技公司报告，中国得到控制，日本央行保持冷静</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:04:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>“滚雪球”衍生品助长中国股市雪崩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/snowball-derivatives-feed-chinas-stock-market-avalanche-2024-01-23/</link><description>中国股市暴跌导致与该国股指相关的衍生品损失数十亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:37:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/snowball-derivatives-feed-chinas-stock-market-avalanche-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国在联合国会议上罕见地接受人权记录审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-undergoes-rare-scrutiny-rights-record-un-meeting-2024-01-23/</link><description>中国在周二的联合国会议上接受了对其人权记录的审查，大多数西方国家呼吁保护新疆维吾尔人并在香港提供更大的自由，而北京方面则认为这些指导是基于谎言的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:06:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-undergoes-rare-scrutiny-rights-record-un-meeting-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国银行在亚洲裁员20人，专注于中国的银行家受影响最大--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-cuts-20-investment-bankers-asia-sources-2024-01-23/</link><description>三名知情人士称，美国银行周二宣布在亚洲裁员约 20 名银行家，原因是中国和香港市场暴跌打压了交易前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-cuts-20-investment-bankers-asia-sources-2024-01-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>